SummaryOfDirectChrtblActyGrp.Description1Txt: GERMANFEST, INC MAINTAINS HERITAGE PARK AND MAKES IT AVAILABLE FOR COMMUNITY AND CULTURAL EVENTS CELEBRATING THE RICH GERMAN HERITAGE OF MUENSTER, TX.
